		"description": "<p>This cosmetic cream contains [[/r 1d8 + 2]] uses when crafted, found, or purchased. When applied to the face, its user may expend a use to have it flawlessly match their skin tone or change it completely. They may expend another use to have the concealer alter the appearance of one of their facial features, such as the shape of their nose or jawline. It costs one use per alteration. Creatures attempting to see through the illusion must succeed on a DC 15 Perception check. The effects of the Clever Concealer last for 8 hours, until it is removed, or it is dispelled by magic such as a @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.hms9kdl2qoqjjrs4]{Dispel Magic} spell.</p>",
